text:
Barbaric place. Serves only their "kind" first even when there is a queue.

Maybe you will get a better experience if you are "same" as them.

Anyway their food comes raw. Ordered curry fishhead and only the outside was cooked. Internals were mucky and yucky. Sent back to the kitchen 2 times but still raw... Come on, you had morning until lunch time to defrost your fish.
One of the  average Indian restaurant in jurong island
Discriminant pricing. 3 of us buy ice cream, each of us charged different for the same type and brand of ice creaming. Found out after we talked among ourselves!
Black chicken soup is very weak... Cost $6.50.. Not worth the price.

Food delivery  no god

Not on time
